Additional environment setup:
- install Pathogen for vim;
- install vim-airline;
- mkdir ~/.vim/undo;
- install Emacs packages:
    Evil mode:
    - M-x package-refresh-contents
    - M-x package-install RET evil

    Org mode:
    - M-x package-refresh-contents
    - M-x list-packages
    - navigate to 'org' and click Install
